{"word":"Fasting","slug":"fasting","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Fasting</b> Observed on occasions of:<br/> - Public calamities<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=1&verse=12'>2Sa 1:12</a> <br/> - Afflictions and Adversities<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=35&verse=13'>Psa 35:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=6&verse=18'>Dan 6:18</a> <br/> - Private afflictions<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=12&verse=16'>2Sa 12:16</a> <br/> - Approaching danger<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=4&verse=16'>Est 4:16</a> <br/> - Ordination of ministers<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=13&verse=3'>Act 13:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=14&verse=23'>Act 14:23</a> <br/> Accompanied by:<br/> - Prayer<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=9&verse=3'>Dan 9:3</a> <br/> - Confession of sin<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=7&verse=6'>1Sa 7:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=9&verse=2'>Neh 9:2</a> <br/> - Humiliation<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=9&verse=18'>Deu 9:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=9&verse=1'>Neh 9:1</a> <br/> During forty days:<br/> - Moses<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=9&verse=9'>Deu 9:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=9&verse=18'>Deu 9:18</a> <br/> - Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=4&verse=2'>Mat 4:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=1&verse=13'>Mar 1:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=4&verse=2'>Luk 4:2</a> <br/> Habitual:<br/> - By John's disciples<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=9&verse=14'>Mat 9:14</a> <br/> - By Anna<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=37'>Luk 2:37</a> <br/> - By Pharisees<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=9&verse=14'>Mat 9:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=2&verse=18'>Mar 2:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=18&verse=12'>Luk 18:12</a> <br/> - By Cornelius<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=10&verse=30'>Act 10:30</a> <br/> - By Paul<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=6&verse=5'>2Co 6:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=11&verse=27'>2Co 11:27</a> <br/> In times of bereavement:<br/> - Of the people of Jabesh-Gilead, for Saul and his sons<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=31&verse=13'>1Sa 31:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=10&verse=12'>1Ch 10:12</a> <br/> - Of David, at the time of Saul's death<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=1&verse=12'>2Sa 1:12</a> <br/> - Of Abner's death<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=3&verse=35'>2Sa 3:35</a> <br/> Prolonged:<br/> - For three weeks, by Daniel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=10&verse=3'>Dan 10:3</a> <br/> - Forty days by Moses<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=24&verse=18'>Exo 24:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=34&verse=28'>Exo 34:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=9&verse=9'>Deu 9:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=9&verse=18'>Deu 9:18</a> <br/> - Forty days by Elijah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=19&verse=8'>1Ki 19:8</a> <br/> - Forty days by Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=4&verse=2'>Mat 4:2</a><br/><a href='S:Humiliation'>Humiliation</a>; <a href='S:Humility'>Humility</a> <br/> Unclassified scriptures relating to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=8&verse=23'>Ezr 8:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=35&verse=13'>Psa 35:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=69&verse=10'>Psa 69:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=58&verse=7'>Isa 58:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=14&verse=12'>Jer 14:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=10&verse=3'>Dan 10:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=29&chapter=1&verse=14'>Joe 1:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=29&chapter=2&verse=13'>Joe 2:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=7&verse=5'>Zec 7:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=8&verse=19'>Zec 8:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=6&verse=18'>Mat 6:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=9&verse=15'>Mat 9:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=17&verse=21'>Mat 17:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=27&verse=9'>Act 27:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=27&verse=34'>Act 27:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=7&verse=5'>1Co 7:5</a><br/> Instances of:<br/> - Of the Israelites:<br/> b in the conflict between the other tribes with the tribe of Benjamin, on account of the wrong suffered by a Levite's concubine<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=20&verse=26'>Jdg 20:26</a><br/> b When they went to Mizpeh for the ark<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=7&verse=6'>1Sa 7:6</a><br/> - Of David:<br/> b at the death of Saul<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=1&verse=12'>2Sa 1:12</a><br/> b During the sickness of the child born to him by Bath-Sheba<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=12&verse=22'>2Sa 12:22</a><br/> b While interceding in prayer for his friends<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=35&verse=13'>Psa 35:13</a><br/> b in his zeal for Zion<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=69&verse=10'>Psa 69:10</a><br/> b in prayer for himself and his adversaries<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=109&verse=4'>Psa 109:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=109&verse=24'>Psa 109:24</a><br/> - Of Ahab, when Elijah prophesied the destruction of himself and his house<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=21&verse=29'>1Ki 21:29</a> <br/> - Of Jehoshaphat, at the time of the invasion of the confederated armies of the Canaanites and Syrians<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=20&verse=3'>2Ch 20:3</a> <br/> - Of Ezra, on account of the idolatrous marriages of the Jews<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=10&verse=6'>Ezr 10:6</a> <br/> - Of Nehemiah, on account of the desolation of Jerusalem and the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=1&verse=4'>Neh 1:4</a> <br/> - Of the Jews:<br/> b When Jeremiah prophesied against Judea and Jerusalem<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=36&verse=9'>Jer 36:9</a><br/> b in Babylon, with prayer for divine deliverance and guidance<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=8&verse=21'>Ezr 8:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=8&verse=23'>Ezr 8:23</a><br/> - Of Darius, when he put Daniel in the lion's den<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=6&verse=18'>Dan 6:18</a> <br/> - Of Daniel:<br/> b on account of the captivity of the people, with prayer for their deliverance<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=9&verse=3'>Dan 9:3</a><br/> b at the time of his vision<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=10&verse=3'>Dan 10:3</a><br/> - Ninevites, when Jonah preached to them<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=32&chapter=3&verse=10'>Jon 3:10</a> <br/> - By Paul, at the time of his conversion<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=9&verse=9'>Act 9:9</a> <br/> - Of the disciples, at the time of the consecration of Barnabas and Saul<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=13&verse=3'>Act 13:3</a> <br/> - Of the consecration of the elders<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=14&verse=23'>Act 14:23</a> "}]}